<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196848>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 12. Head, anterior view. 1. Acanthophotopsis falciformis; 2. Acrophotopsis campylognatha; 3. Odontophotopsis acmaea; 4. O. armata; 5. O. aufidia; 6. O. bellona; 7. O. biramosa; 8. O. clypeata; 9. O. inconspicua; 10. O. mamata; 11. O. melicausa; and 12. O. quadrispinosa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196848/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196853>
    dc:description "FIGURES 44 – 48. Sphaeropthalma mankelli, sp. nov.: 44. Head, anterior view; 45. Habitus; and 46. Apex of wing. Acrophotopsis campylognatha: 47. genitalia, dorsal view (scale 0.5 mm) and 48. Close up of cuspis (scale 0.2 mm) (Fig. 47. from Pitts & McHugh 2002)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196853/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196849>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 24. Head, anterior view; except ventral view 17. 13. Odontophotopsis serca; 14. O. setifera; 15. Sphaeropthalma. amphion; 16. S. angulifera; 17. S. angulifera; 18. S. arota; 19. S. becki; 20. S. blakeii; 21. S. difficilis; 22. S. ferruginea; 23. S. ignacio; and 24. S. macswaini." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196849/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

